high_descs: walk to face counter to right of fridge
pick up butter knife from counter
walk to face kitchen island counter above oven
put knife into cup on counter
pick up cup from counter
turn to face sink
put cup in sink basin
anns.task_desc: put cup and knife into sink

high_descs: Turn to the left and move towards the counter on the right past the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn around and move forward, then turning left to face the island counter above the oven.
Place the butter knife into the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup with the butter knife inside.
Turn left and move toward the sink.
Place the cup with the butter knife inside into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Clean up the butter knife and cup into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the left. Turn to the right and face the counter.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the left. Turn to the left and walk around the island to the other side. Turn left again to face the island.
Place the knife inside the cup on the island
Pick up the cup and knife from the island.
Turn left and then go straight then turn left again to face the sink.
Place the cup and knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the cup and knife to the sink.
